						<summary>

						<p>On the north wall of the kitchen in the Bhaktavatsalēśvara temple, right of entrance.</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">Bhūpatirāya: Śaka 1330 = 1408 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records the gift of 32 cows and a bull for a perpetual lamp to the temple of Tirukkaḻukkuṉṟamuḍaiya-nayiṉār by Tirukkaḻukkuṉṟamuḍaiyān of Neṟkuḷam. </p>						

